    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Promise 2.8.0]]></title>
    <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>
<p>Mark <code>FulfilledPromise</code>, <code>RejectedPromise</code> and <code>LazyPromise</code> as deprecated for Promise v2 (and remove for Promise v3).<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="459181492" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise/issues/143" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise/pull/143/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise/pull/143">#143</a> and <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="577487588" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise/issues/165" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise/pull/165/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise/pull/165">#165</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-text-html-php"><pre>// deprecated
$fulfilled = new React\Promise\FulfilledPromise($value);
$rejected = new React\Promise\RejectedPromise($reason);

// recommended alternatives
$fulfilled = React\Promise\resolve($value);
$rejected = React\Promise\reject($reason);</pre></div>
</li>
<li>
<p>Fix: Fix checking whether cancellable promise is an object and avoid possible warning.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="615161685" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise/issues/168" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise/pull/168/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise/pull/168">#168</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/smscr/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/smscr">@smscr</a> and <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/jsor/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/jsor">@jsor</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Improve documentation and add docblocks to functions and interfaces.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="396878297" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise/issues/135" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise/pull/135/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise/pull/135">#135</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/CharlotteDunois/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/CharlotteDunois">@CharlotteDunois</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Add <code>.gitattributes</code> to exclude dev files from exports.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="530762040" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise/issues/154" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise/pull/154/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise/pull/154">#154</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/reedy/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/reedy">@reedy</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Improve test suite, run tests on PHP 7.4 and update PHPUnit test setup.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="575313779" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise/issues/163" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise/pull/163/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise/pull/163">#163</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
</li>
</ul>]]></summary>
