    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Socket 1.4.0]]></title>
    <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>A major new feature release, see <a href="https://clue.engineering/2020/introducing-ipv6-for-reactphp" rel="nofollow"><strong>release announcement</strong></a>.</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Feature: Add IPv6 support to <code>Connector</code> (implement "Happy Eyeballs" algorithm to support IPv6 probing).<br>
IPv6 support is turned on by default, use new <code>happy_eyeballs</code> option in <code>Connector</code> to toggle behavior.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="415336445" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/196" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/196/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/196">#196</a>, <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="577351300" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/224" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/224/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/224">#224</a> and <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="579243592" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/225" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/225/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/225">#225</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/WyriHaximus/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/WyriHaximus">@WyriHaximus</a> and <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Feature: Default to using DNS cache (with max 256 entries) for <code>Connector</code>.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="579375999" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/226" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/226/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/226">#226</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Add <code>.gitattributes</code> to exclude dev files from exports and some minor code style fixes.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="530763455" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/219" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/219/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/219">#219</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/reedy/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/reedy">@reedy</a> and <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="525991391" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/218" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/218/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/218">#218</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/mmoreram/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/mmoreram">@mmoreram</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Improve test suite to fix failing test cases when using new DNS component,<br>
significantly improve test performance by awaiting events instead of sleeping,<br>
exclude TLS 1.3 test on PHP 7.3, run tests on PHP 7.4 and simplify test matrix.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="469718878" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/208" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/208/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/208">#208</a>, <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="481098218" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/209" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/209/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/209">#209</a>, <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="481102160" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/210" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/210/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/210">#210</a>, <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="524032637" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/217" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/217/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/217">#217</a> and <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="575460798" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/223" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/223/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/223">#223</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
</li>
</ul>]]></summary>
