    <title type="html"><![CDATA[EventLoop 1.1.1]]></title>
    <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>
<p>Fix: Fix reporting connection refused errors with <code>ExtUvLoop</code> on Linux and <code>StreamSelectLoop</code> on Windows.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="543263503" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/event-loop/issues/207" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/event-loop/pull/207/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/event-loop/pull/207">#207</a> and <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="544149993" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/event-loop/issues/208" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/event-loop/pull/208/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/event-loop/pull/208">#208</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Fix: Fix unsupported EventConfig and <code>SEGFAULT</code> on shutdown with <code>ExtEventLoop</code> on Windows.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="542964895" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/event-loop/issues/205" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/event-loop/pull/205/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/event-loop/pull/205">#205</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Fix: Prevent interval overflow for timers very far in the future with <code>ExtUvLoop</code>.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="445966113" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/event-loop/issues/196" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/event-loop/pull/196/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/event-loop/pull/196">#196</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/PabloKowalczyk/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/PabloKowalczyk">@PabloKowalczyk</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Fix: Check PCNTL functions for signal support instead of PCNTL extension with <code>StreamSelectLoop</code>.<br>
