    <title type="html"><![CDATA[DNS 1.0.0]]></title>
    <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>First stable LTS release, now following <a href="https://semver.org/" rel="nofollow">SemVer</a>.<br>
We'd like to emphasize that this component is production ready and battle-tested.<br>
We plan to support all long-term support (LTS) releases for at least 24 months,<br>
so you have a rock-solid foundation to build on top of.</li>
</ul>
<p>This update involves a number of BC breaks due to dropped support for<br>
deprecated functionality and some internal API cleanup. We've tried hard to<br>
avoid BC breaks where possible and minimize impact otherwise. We expect that<br>
most consumers of this package will actually not be affected by any BC<br>
breaks, see below for more details:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>BC break: Delete all deprecated APIs, use <code>Query</code> objects for <code>Message</code> questions<br>
instead of nested arrays and increase code coverage to 100%.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="465771042" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/issues/130" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/dns/pull/130/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/pull/130">#130</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>BC break: Move <code>$nameserver</code> from <code>ExecutorInterface</code> to <code>UdpTransportExecutor</code>,<br>
remove advanced/internal <code>UdpTransportExecutor</code> args for <code>Parser</code>/<code>BinaryDumper</code> and<br>
add API documentation for <code>ExecutorInterface</code>.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="466759823" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/issues/135" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/dns/pull/135/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/pull/135">#135</a>, <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="466797146" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/issues/137" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/dns/pull/137/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/pull/137">#137</a> and <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="466886290" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/issues/138" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/dns/pull/138/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/pull/138">#138</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>BC break: Replace <code>HeaderBag</code> attributes with simple <code>Message</code> properties.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="465915799" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/issues/132" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/dns/pull/132/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/pull/132">#132</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>BC break: Mark all <code>Record</code> attributes as required, add documentation vs <code>Query</code>.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="466784724" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/issues/136" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/dns/pull/136/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/pull/136">#136</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>BC break: Mark all classes as final to discourage inheritance<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="466693315" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/issues/134" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/dns/pull/134/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/dns/pull/134">#134</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/WyriHaximus/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/WyriHaximus">@WyriHaximus</a>)</p>
</li>
</ul>]]></summary>
